The 'mutation catalyst' almost always lowers item value or makes it negative, so use it with extreme caution or only if other options are exhausted. 'Ultra-grown flying' hybrids made from two small creatures (like bee + butterfly) seem to yield the highest values, sometimes reaching 35. Other hybrids often peak around 30.
